headline: GTA Online
subtitle: MOD SQUAD
content:
Attention MC Presidents: It’s time to accelerate club takings. Stock your bar with Sindy’s help and open your doors to LS’s finest leather-clad patrons. Custom Bike Shop owners can now share their love of two wheels by modifying and delivering bikes to paying customers.

Don’t like clean money? No sweat –there are brand new Clubhouse Contracts so you can keep your hands dirty.
